{"id": 2449, "genre": 1001, "title": "小时候你家都有什么奇怪的禁令？", "description": "不许养小动物，见到野猫要躲开来，不然会生不治之症……（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3949, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180703140807poD4hNkIVOJY8RX7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-23T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 294144, "content": "牙掉了要扔到房顶上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411512}, {"id": 294915, "content": "不能敲打碗 筷子不能立在饭中间 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415484}, {"id": 294148, "content": "壁虎咬人治不好       ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333265}, {"id": 295428, "content": "指月亮?耳朵会被割掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417791}, {"id": 296196, "content": "吃鹌鹑蛋会长斑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419153}, {"id": 294149, "content": "不准上上下下左右左右BABA", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122304}, {"id": 295173, "content": "摩托车头盔不能放地上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416516}, {"id": 296197, "content": "不许吃零食，不能吃肯德基等油炸食品(´ . .̫ . `)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423033}, {"id": 294150, "content": "坐着不能抖腿，吃饭不能吧唧嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411533}, {"id": 296454, "content": "要有礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421471}, {"id": 294152, "content": "睡觉开窗会嘴歪眼斜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382868}, {"id": 294153, "content": "看见下面有说吃西瓜不吐籽会发芽，这真的是我童年阴影。但自从我知道不会发芽之后，吃西瓜再也不吐籽了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031737}, {"id": 294154, "content": "不能玩算盘，会不识数", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410124}, {"id": 295434, "content": "阿姨你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647516}, {"id": 295946, "content": "走路不准把外套敞着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422015}, {"id": 298250, "content": "生气的时候不能拍桌子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108770}, {"id": 294155, "content": "骑狗烂裤裆(〜￣△￣)〜", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968367}, {"id": 295435, "content": "打嗝的时候，大人说一句你吃屎吗？然后你说是，然后就不会打嗝了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417831}, {"id": 294156, "content": "吃饭不能剩米粒，不然以后娶的媳妇脸上会有麻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387848}, {"id": 295436, "content": "有一种鸡内脏，叫鸡忘记，吃了会忘事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417831}, {"id": 294157, "content": "不准出工厂大院的门。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243520}, {"id": 294158, "content": "挂在阳台的裤子不能钻过去不然长不高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411583}, {"id": 294414, "content": "吃饭的时候不要说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413303}, {"id": 295183, "content": "不听话就扔到外面给大老狼吃?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083754}, {"id": 296463, "content": "见人必笑，熟人必打招呼，否则一巴掌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424219}, {"id": 294160, "content": "不许去水边，有水鬼拉人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364037}, {"id": 295698, "content": "不能说“扯”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407164}, {"id": 294163, "content": "吃饭的时候筷子掉了意味着将来会挨打。。。所以我每次筷子掉了都会主动叫别人拍我手掌两下“破除诅咒”，而且我直到现在都还保留着这个恶趣味的迷信¯\\_(ツ)_/¯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443174}, {"id": 294164, "content": "不可以谈论国事", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 294165, "content": "坐在背篓上会拉不来屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410783}, {"id": 294166, "content": "把水果的籽吃到肚子里会从头上长出来→_→我曾经居然深信不疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410783}, {"id": 294422, "content": "晚上不能掏耳朵不然会变聋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413481}, {"id": 294167, "content": "过年不准说不吉利的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1409284}, {"id": 294168, "content": "穿凉鞋必须穿袜子   虽然现在感觉有点时尚   但小时候真的觉得土到不穿凉鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411648}, {"id": 294169, "content": "捡的钱一定要买吃的吃掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359635}, {"id": 294170, "content": "筷子不能直接插在饭上面 房间门不能关上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990375}, {"id": 294171, "content": "不能在屋子里打伞，房子会漏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411670}, {"id": 294172, "content": "不让吃鱼籽，据说吃了以后不会数数", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411676}, {"id": 295196, "content": "拉屎的时候不许吃东西！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415913}, {"id": 294173, "content": "吃饭不能不扶碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686950}, {"id": 296221, "content": "吃鱼子会变蠢，学不好数学", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423158}, {"id": 294174, "content": "躺着吃饭肚子会歪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480024}, {"id": 294942, "content": "女孩不能分筷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415562}, {"id": 294175, "content": "骑狗烂裤裆", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 294176, "content": "晚上八点半之前要回家。\n玩电脑只能周六周日各一个小时。\n尽管如此我还是深度近视了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411696}, {"id": 294177, "content": "在家里，不能撑伞，会长不高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411701}, {"id": 294689, "content": "女性不能上桌吃饭 要在厨房或者搬小板凳在外面吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414732}, {"id": 294178, "content": "周日到周四(第二天要上学)，必须八点就去睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411702}, {"id": 294179, "content": "吃饭的时候，食指不可以翘起来指天上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411701}, {"id": 294691, "content": "不能摸麻雀 否则写字手会抖", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414732}]}